overview:
Wedding Retouching is a digital photo retouching service for wedding photographers, professional or amateur.

Our services include recomposing your photo, removing unwanted shadows and confetti or even people. We can remove creases from clothes and colour black and white photos and turn images into silhouettes, or create a sense of mood or tranquillity. If you missed a group shot we can even combine two or more photos together.

If you are a professional photographer or if it’s your first wedding photo shoot, Wedding Retouching will help you achieve your goals to capture that perfect wedding. No job is considered too small and every retouch will be given the care and attention, to ensure your client will have the photos of their wedding the way they remember it.
